    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个危机四伏的超现实世界。你可以选择避开危险，正面应对，或者寻找其他方法解决问题。真相就藏在某个地方，只要你能找到它。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态冲突解决方式！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以选择应对每场遭遇战的方法：与敌人战斗、躲避危险、通过谈判化解冲突，亦或是另辟蹊径？你的每一个决策都将决定旅程的发展方向并影响结果，从而带来多重结局。体验多种游戏类型的独特融合。参与节奏紧凑的策略战斗，感受毛骨悚然的恐怖元素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/fab5b12eba4975989f054afd4382eaf3.poster.avif?t=1765950477\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/fab5b12eba4975989f054afd4382eaf3.webm?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/fab5b12eba4975989f054afd4382eaf3.mp4?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >广阔世界任你探索！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个美梦与噩梦交织的世界。冒险穿越充满怪异现象和隐藏秘密的诡异、超现实环境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/da620e3d85b9eeab263cf329cfc6ae6f.poster.avif?t=1765950477\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/da620e3d85b9eeab263cf329cfc6ae6f.webm?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/da620e3d85b9eeab263cf329cfc6ae6f.mp4?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >深度自定义、装备、伙伴与宠物系统！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你找到的物品能让你在战斗中获得独特能力，实现灵活的自定义。伙伴和宠物各自拥有特殊的战斗机制，可以改变战斗的方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/090a495e15a5bdd1a259bbf5d21c7f8e.poster.avif?t=1765950477\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/090a495e15a5bdd1a259bbf5d21c7f8e.webm?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/090a495e15a5bdd1a259bbf5d21c7f8e.mp4?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >怪诞的剧情！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对你的恐惧，在丰富的叙事中揭开真相。与引人入胜的角色交互，探索有趣的世界，体验离奇的故事情节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/e2b5573f64b39c2af904e50babda01dc.poster.avif?t=1765950477\" width=600 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/e2b5573f64b39c2af904e50babda01dc.webm?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1871640/extras/e2b5573f64b39c2af904e50babda01dc.mp4?t=1765950477\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种玩法选择！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索者：压力较小、专注于剧情体验与探索的玩法。（类似《梦日记》）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险者：兼具角色扮演与生存恐怖元素的平衡玩法。（类似《地球冒险》/《传说之下》）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >幸存者：有着永久死亡设定的硬核生存恐怖玩法。（类似《恐惧与饥饿》）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
